# <%= projectName %>

Spring Boot 4.0.5 backend service scaffolded with [Forge CLI](https://github.com/example/forge-cli).

## Prerequisites

- Java 21 (LTS)
- Maven 3.9+
- Docker (for local SQL Server and TestContainers)
<% if (messaging === 'Kafka') { %>- Apache Kafka (local: Docker Compose or Confluent Platform)
<% } %>

## Quick Start

```bash
# Start SQL Server locally (Docker)
docker run -e "ACCEPT_EULA=Y" -e "SA_PASSWORD=LocalDev123!" \
  -p 1433:1433 -d mcr.microsoft.com/mssql/server:2022-latest
<% if (messaging === 'Kafka') { %>
# Start Kafka locally (Docker)
docker compose up -d kafka
<% } %>

# Run the application
./mvnw spring-boot:run
```

## Building

```bash
./mvnw clean package
```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Requires Docker (TestContainers starts SQL Server automatically)
./mvnw test
```

## Docker

```bash
docker build -t <%= projectName %> .
docker run -p 8080:8080 \
  -e DATABASE_URL=jdbc:sqlserver://host:1433 \
  -e DATABASE_USERNAME=sa \
  -e DATABASE_PASSWORD=secret \
  <%= projectName %>
```

## API Documentation

- Swagger UI: [http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html](http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html)
- OpenAPI spec: [http://localhost:8080/v3/api-docs](http://localhost:8080/v3/api-docs)

## Environment Profiles

| Profile | Purpose | Database |
|---------|---------|----------|
| `local` | Developer machine | SQL Server localhost:1433 |
| `dev` | Shared development | SQL Server (env vars) |
| `sit` | System integration testing | SQL Server (env vars) |
| `uat` | User acceptance testing | SQL Server (env vars) |
| `prod` | Production | SQL Server (env vars, Key Vault) |
| `test` | Automated tests | SQL Server (TestContainers) |

## Project Structure

```
src/main/java/<%= groupId.replace(/\./g, '/') %>/
├── config/          # Spring configuration classes
├── controller/      # REST controllers
├── service/         # Business logic
├── repository/      # Data access (Spring Data JPA)
├── domain/
│   ├── entity/      # JPA entities
│   ├── enums/       # Domain enumerations
│   └── event/       # Domain events
├── dto/
│   ├── request/     # Inbound DTOs
│   └── response/    # Outbound DTOs
├── exception/       # Exception hierarchy + global handler
├── mapper/          # Entity <-> DTO mappers
├── client/          # External service clients
├── util/            # Utilities (CorrelationIdFilter, MaskingUtil)
├── messaging/       # Message producers and consumers
└── specification/   # JPA Specifications for dynamic queries
```

## Key Decisions

- **Database:** SQL Server (Azure SQL in production)
- **Auth:** <%= authPattern %>
- **Messaging:** <%= messaging %>
- **Observability:** OpenTelemetry + Logstash JSON logging
- **Resilience:** Resilience4j (circuit breaker, retry, bulkhead)
